            "title": "黑期升34點     ADR低水1點  恒地高水",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期升34點或0.14%，報23902。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恒指昨天收市低水1點，報23905點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"恒基地產官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/00012-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"恒基地產官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/00012-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">恒基地產官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新東方(09901) ADR較香港收市價高水2.4%，折合37.65港元 ; 恒基地產(00012) ADR較香港收市價高水2.1%，折合24.82港元 ; 舜宇(02382) ADR較香港收市價高水0.8%%，折合63.82港元 。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報93.52元，較香港收市價高0.56%; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣67.14%，較香港收市價高水0.4% ;港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣404.31元，較香港收市價低0.2% ; 中國平安(02318) ADR收市折合港幣46.29元，較香港收市價高.2%</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690) ADR較香港收市價高0.5%，折合145.16港元 ; 騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣515.95元，較港收市價較港收市價高.2% ; 阿里巴巴(09988) ADR較香港收市價低水0.5%，折合117.65元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報23822點，升26點，較昨日恒指收市23906點，低水85點，成交21071張。國指夜市期指收報8647點，較昨日國指收市低水38點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14988180-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%8d%8734%e9%bb%9e-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b41%e9%bb%9e-%e6%81%92%e5%9c%b0%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-06 08:55:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "新世界 滶晨折實入場價850.3萬   呎價18688起",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14986736&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新世界發展(00017)與帝國集團、資本策略地產(00497)、麗新發展(00488)及港鐵(00066)發展的黃竹坑站港島南岸「DEEP WATER PAVILIA 滶晨」今日發第一張價單。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">第一張價單涉及101伙，包括4伙4房戶、2伙3房戶、95伙2房戶。實用面積455-1261呎。提供最高折扣20%計算，價單折實售價850.3-3724.7萬，折實呎價18688至29538元。折實平均呎價20932元。折實總值約11.05億。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首張價單中，78伙折實售價全數低於1000萬元，68伙折實呎價2萬元或以下。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">展銷廳及示範單位提早正式明天開放予公眾參觀，最快下周開售。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新世界發展營業及市務部總監何家欣表示，加推之後的價單有提價空間。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14986736-%e6%96%b0%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c-%e6%bb%b6%e6%99%a8%e6%8a%98%e5%af%a6%e5%85%a5%e5%a0%b4%e5%83%b9850-3%e8%90%ac-%e5%91%8e%e5%83%b918688%e8%b5%b7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/pp_new-flat-transaction_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-06 08:45:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "宇晴軒中層2房650萬元易手    原業主帳面獲利近一倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14986447&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">香港置業西九龍星匯居分行日前促成一宗宇晴軒的2房單位買賣成交，新買家斥650萬元入市，實用呎價約14606元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述成交單位為宇晴軒7座中層E室，實用面積約445平方呎，屬2房間隔，向北望園景，該行指，業主最初叫價約680萬元，放盤約2個月後有洽詢，雙方經議價後以650萬元成交，實用呎價約14606元。據悉，新買家為租客，因供樓成本與租金相距收窄，故轉租為買。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">資料顯示，原業於2009年12月以約329萬元購入上述單位，是次轉手帳賺約321萬元，物業升值近1倍。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14986447-%e5%ae%87%e6%99%b4%e8%bb%92%e4%b8%ad%e5%b1%a42%e6%88%bf650%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%98%93%e6%89%8b-%e5%8e%9f%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e5%b8%b3%e9%9d%a2%e7%8d%b2%e5%88%a9%e8%bf%91%e4%b8%80%e5%80%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-06 08:45:52",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "太古城錄本月首宗成交  三房戶885萬元承接     2019年貨貶值約3成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14986428&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美聯物業太古城-太古城道分行剛促成太古城6月份市場上首宗成交，一個富山閣中層A室單位，實用面積約690呎，獲用家以885萬元市價承接，折合實用呎價約12826元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原業主於2019年持貨至今轉手帳面貶值約3成，與大市相若。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">剛促成的成交為三房戶型，原業主叫價約900萬元，並獲同區客垂青，見樓價合理，而議價後終以約885萬元易手。原業主於2019年2月以約1268萬元購入物業，是次轉手帳面蝕讓約383萬元或貶值約30%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14986428-%e5%a4%aa%e5%8f%a4%e5%9f%8e%e9%8c%84%e6%9c%ac%e6%9c%88%e9%a6%96%e5%ae%97%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e4%b8%89%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6885%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%89%bf%e6%8e%a5-2019%e5%b9%b4%e8%b2%a8%e8%b2%b6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-06 08:45:54",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價高收近1%　中美元首通話帶動市場氣氛",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">油價反彈近1%，受到中美元首通話的消息帶動。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-4.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-4.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油報每桶63.37美元，升52美仙，升幅0.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收市報每桶65.34美元，升48美仙，升幅0.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上星期美國汽油和蒸餾油庫存大幅增加，加上沙特阿拉伯將針對亞洲原油買家的價格，下調至近2個月以來最低，都限制油價升幅。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14988090-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6%e8%bf%911%e3%80%80%e4%b8%ad%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e9%a6%96%e9%80%9a%e8%a9%b1%e5%b8%b6%e5%8b%95%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e6%b0%a3%e6%b0%9b",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094825_OilPrice_AP_source-ap_-2-1-1-1-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-06 08:45:45",
